# lag / lead & running aggregates

## Offset — look back / forward

- **`lag(col, n, default)`** — `n` rows **back** · **`lead(col, n, default)`** — `n` rows **forward**
- Returns the default (or `null`) at the partition boundary
- For deltas: "days since previous transaction," "time to next event"

## Running aggregates — the frame

- **`rowsBetween`** — physical **row** positions
- **`rangeBetween`** — **value** range of the order-by column (e.g. ±7 days)

## Three frames to memorize

- **Cumulative** — `rowsBetween(unboundedPreceding, currentRow)`
- **Trailing N** — `rowsBetween(-N, currentRow)` · **Centered** — `rowsBetween(-N, N)`
